file_content.text: Excellent! I was just wondering what I could do to please you!
I will perform according to your exacting specifications, master!
A task just for you? Oh, thank you, master!
Leave everything to me, master. I will not disappoint you!
The results are much better than they appear, master. You'll see!
There were complications, master. Please don't deactivate me!
I seem to have outdone myself, master. I think you'll be quite pleased.
Master, I deliver to you something beyond perfection. You deserve nothing less.
